The '''Nanth'ri Pirates''' were a group of space [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] who plundered the [[Nanth'ri Route]] under [[Celis Mott]]. After Mott's disappearance, the group evaporated.

==Behind the scenes==
In the "[[Rebel Privateers!]]" article in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 2|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 2]], '''Nanth'ri''' is spelled '''Nanthri''' (without the apostrophe).

